src: Using a Heat Limiter, the temperature of a machine or heat cable can be tightly controlled. It connects to a heat cable in the front and back. It only allows heat to flow when the temperature of the output, in degrees kelvin, is lower than the redstone (or Ratiator) signal strength received. This can be used as a temperature regulator of sorts, to keep the output heat cable at right around the temperature set via a Ratiator, provided abundent heat is provided into the input side.

src:
Now. Now I can truly begin to use impetus.
Using the schematics I had previously created for the Void Siphon, I was able to modify the design so I could create the fundamental devices that can automatically collect, transport, resonate and distribute impetus. I shall cover how can one properly set up an impetus power system, and to do this I shall break it all down into separate parts that cover the different concepts, tools and devices involved.
Before I begin, however, I feel I must note that when it comes to learning something new, more often than not the best way to understand something is to experiment with it physically. I should also note that impetus is complex topic for one to understand, and I would not be surprised if I happen to forget certain parts or get confused about impetus power mechanisms. Thus, if I am at all confused by what I am detailing, I might find it helpful to create and experiment with a few simple impetus energy setups so to better understand the principles involved firsthand. I suppose that I will have to see whether I prefer careful study or practical experimentation in order to fully understand this complicated and dangerous topic.§lCharged Impetus§r
Previously I only had access to impetus fairly indirectly, through the void seeds it created and the impetus stored in conductors attached to gauntlets. But with my new discoveries I am now able to gather impetus in a different more energetic form. I am calling this new form of impetus 'Charged Impetus'. I shall cover the distinction between the two.
Normal impetus can be seen as lines of starry void trailing through the air, and is usually directly pulled from a flux rift. It is what I have been using up until now and is what void siphons and impetus conductors use. Devices accessing normal impetus tend to be able to idly draw it from an impetus source, again, this usually being in the form of a flux rift. Notably, it is harmless for one to touch normal impetus trails… at least, probably, but they do at least seem to pass through me without any damage done.
Charged impetus, however, is more volatile and therefore has a great deal more potential use. By making it take this charged form, I can transfer larger amounts of impetus over longer distances. It is what will power my planned specialised machinery, and can be seen in the world as beams of energy, which vary from faint to bright depending on how much charged impetus is being sent through them. Another difference from normal impetus is that charged impetus must be specifically directed to devices that use it, as opposed to drawing it from a nearby rift. I shall detail later on in this entry how to create charged impetus.
For the sake of safety, I should note that an active beam of charged impetus has enough compacted energy to be rather deadly, and if I am caught between one then I will be hurt. Inactive beams, however, are safe. An inactive beam can be seen as faint wisps of energy, while an active beam glows bright and can be clearly seen.§lImpetus Nodes§r
Blocks placed in the world that connect to beams of charged impetus are collectively referred to as 'impetus nodes'. To clarify: they have no relation to aura nodes. It does not matter whether a device creates, uses, or simply transfers charged impetus, if it connects to charged impetus beams in one form or another then it is classified as an impetus node.
Impetus nodes have set numbers of input and output slots, which dictate how many beams of charged impetus can feed into and be sent out of them. Impetus nodes, therefore, can be designed so to transfer energy from one to the other, so a source of charged impetus can output energy into a node, and this node can output energy into another node, and so on and so forth. Different nodes have different numbers of input and output slots, for instance a device that creates charged impetus will only have output slots, a device that transfers charged impetus will have both inputs and outputs, and a device that uses charged impetus will only have input slots.§lImpetus Resonator§r
With impetus nodes having been detailed, there still needs to be a way to define how impetus nodes are connected to one another. For such a purpose, I have designed the Impetus Resonator.
The Impetus Resonator is a tool which can modify the connections an impetus node has. By holding the device in hand and then sneaking and right-clicking an impetus node of any kind, said node will be clearly highlighted in blue and selected for modification. If I sneak right-click the same node again, it will be deselected.
With an impetus node selected, I can then connect it to another node by right-clicking without sneaking on said other node. By doing this, the first node has been set to output energy into the second one, taking up an output slot on the first node and an input slot on the second. If I right-click the second node again, then the connection will be removed. To send energy from one node into multiple other ones, then I simply select the first node via sneak right-click and then right-click all the other nodes one-by-one. I should keep in mind the slot limitations when doing this, however. Also of note is that impetus beams can only travel so far, at a distance of around eight meters, and they cannot travel through opaque walls. Glass or other transparent materials will permit impetus beams to pass through them, however. I will need to ensure that impetus nodes are kept fairly close together and that they are not obstructed by walls in order to link them together properly.
If I select an impetus node that already has connections defined, then I can also see these connections visualised. Any nodes that feed impetus into the selected node are highlighted in red, and any nodes the selected node sends impetus out to are highlighted in green. In the special case of a node being both an input and output of the selected node, it will be highlighted in purple. If I am at all uncertain, I can also see in which direction impetus will travel based on which direction the beams are flowing.
While the Impetus Resonator can define how nodes are connected to one another, very little will happen if no charged impetus is actually being fed into the system, which is where the Impetus Drainer comes in.§lImpetus Drainer§r
The Impetus Drainer is an important impetus node that creates charged impetus energy when placed next to a flux rift. Based on the Void Siphon, it has a dense piece of void metal on top which draws in normal impetus (fortunately, the nether star was not needed here, since the siphon's only use for it is to coalesce normal impetus into void seeds), and using a rotating mechanism it charges the impetus and transmits it into an impetus jewel at its centre. It can therefore be seen as the heart of a charged impetus generation system. When the Drainer draws impetus out of a rift, the rift in question will gradually begin to shrink and become unstable, as with the Void Siphon. Draining a smaller rift will result in it drawing less impetus than if the rift was larger. Therefore, I should ensure that I keep an eye on the rift I am draining to ensure that it remains stable and sizeable.
The device itself has one impetus beam output slot and no inputs, since it creates charged impetus. Therefore, to send energy out of it and into other impetus nodes, I only need to sneak right-click it with the Impetus Resonator and then right-click on the other nodes in question.
If I wish to disable the device, I only need to provide it with a redstone signal. This will stop the device from draining any nearby rifts and from creating impetus, so I can use this to ensure that I do not drain a flux rift too much.§lImpetus Relay§r
Probably the simplest type of impetus node, the Impetus Relay is simply a way to transport beams of impetus from one place to another. It has two input slots and two output slots, so I have some room to tinker with routing in my energy transport systems.§lImpetus Diffuser§r
This device can be seen as the inverse of the Impetus Drainer, since it takes in charged impetus and diffuses normal impetus from the top. Therefore, it can be used to power any devices that drain flux rifts directly, such as gauntlets with impetus resonators attached or void siphons. It has one input slot and no output slots, since it is a device that consumes charged impetus.
I should note that the Diffuser cannot power the Impetus Drainer, since that could create feedback problems where normal impetus is converted to charged impetus, which is converted back to normal via the diffuser, which is then is sent back into the drainer which converts it to charged, which is sent back to the diffuser, etc.
Of note is that using this device to power normal impetus devices will in fact be better for them than having them drain a rift directly. The charging process actively improves the efficiency of impetus creation, so it should be well worth the effort to use my new impetus power systems even with my older machines.
As with the Drainer, I can turn the device off with a redstone signal, which will therefore prevent it from powering normal impetus devices.
This covers the basics of charged impetus power systems. Despite my progress, I know that I have much more to learn and create, both with devices that transmit impetus but also those that use it.
There is so much potential here, my mind is spinning with so many possibilities…
target:
终于迎来了这一刻。现在我可以真正开始运用元动能量了。
借助我以前为虚空吸管设计的原理图，我得以对其设计进行调整，于是制造了能够自动收集、传输、共振和分发元动能量的基本装置。我将详细记述如何建立一个元动能量系统，为此我将把所有内容分成几个不同的部分进行阐述，这些内容涵盖了所涉及的不同的概念，工具和设备。
在我开始之前，我觉得必须强调一件事，那就是在学习新知时，理解知识的最好办法就是亲身实践进行试验。我还需要强调的是，元动学是一个艰深晦涩的主题，因此如果我碰巧忘记了一部分知识或者对元动能量的机制感到困惑，我丝毫不会惊讶。所以，如果我对自己所提及的细节感到不解，那么我应该会发现尝试制造并试验一些简单的元动能量装置会大有助益，如此一来即可更好地亲身体会其中所涉及的原理。我想我必须弄清楚自己倾向于谨慎的理论研究还是亲身进行试验，以便充分理解这门复杂且危险的科目。§l蕴变元动能量§r
以前我只能间接地接触元动能量，通过利用它制取的虚空种子以及附加在护手上的电池中的元动能量来使用它。但凭借我的全新发现，我可以收集一种新形式的元动能量，这种元动能量不同以往，更具活力。我将这种新型元动能量称为“蕴变元动能量”。我将会阐述两者间的不同。
一般的元动能量可被视为繁星密布的虚空划过空气时留下的轨迹线，通常可从咒波裂隙中提取出来。它就是我直到目前一直在使用的元动能量，我往常会用虚空吸管和元动能量电池来使用它。能够接触到一般元动能量的设备倾向于闲散缓慢地从元动能量中抽取能量，再提一次，这种能量源通常是以咒波裂隙的形式存在。值得一提的是，触碰一般元动能量的轨迹束不会造成伤害……至少，也许是不会有害的，但它们至少看起来在穿过我时没有造成任何损害。
但蕴变元动能量则要更加动荡易变，也因此更具潜能。通过使元动能量采用这种蕴含变动的形式，我能将更多的元动能量传输到更远的距离。蕴变元动能量将会为我计划中专门制造的机械提供能量，这会形成可见的能量束，其外观会在微弱到明亮之间发生变化，其亮度取决于传递了多少蕴变元动能量。蕴变元动能量与一般元动能量的另一个区别是，它必须被导向使用它的设备，而非从附近的裂隙中抽取。我将在随后的条目中详细阐述如何产生蕴变元动能量。
出于安全起见，我应当注意，激活的蕴变元动能量束中具有高浓度的能量，因此极为致命，我如果触碰到它们就会受到伤害。不过未激活的能量束则是安全地。未激活的能量束看起来就像是一缕微弱的能流，而激活的能量束则会发出醒目的光芒。§l元动节点§r
放置在世界之中且与蕴变元动能量相连的方块统称为“元动节点”。需要澄清的是：它们与灵气节点无关。无论一件设备是在产生、使用或是传输蕴变元动能量，只要它与蕴变元动能量束的任意一种形式相连，那么它就属于元动节点。
元动节点具有一定数目的输入和输出槽，这决定了节点能够接收和发射多少道蕴变元动能量束。因此，可以通过设计节点系统使能量在元动节点间传输，如此一来蕴变元动能量源可将能量输出到一个节点，而该节点则能将能量输出到另一个节点，依此类推。不同的节点输入和输出槽的数量也不同，例如产生蕴变元动能量的装置仅有输出槽，而传输蕴变元动能量的设备则同时具备输入和输出槽，使用蕴变元动能量的设备则只有输入槽。
§l元动谐振器§r
在详细阐述元动节点的机理后，还需要一种方法来界定元动节点间如何相互连接。为此我设计了元动谐振器。
元动谐振器是一种能够调整节点间连接的工具。将这件设备拿在手中，然后潜行并右击任意类型的元动节点，该节点就会呈现出蓝色的高亮选框，同时被选定以做调整。如果我对同一个节点再次潜行并右击，则会取消选定。
选中元动节点后，我可以在非潜行的情况下右击其他节点，以将该节点连接至被右击的节点。这样一来，第一个节点便被设置为将能量输出到第二个节点，这会占用第一个节点的一个输出槽和第二个节点的一个输入槽。如果我再次右击第二个节点，那么连接就将被移除。要将一个节点的能量输出到多个节点中，我只需通过潜行并右击选中第一个节点，然后逐个右击所有其他的节点。不过在这么做时，我应该留意节点槽位的上限值。还需要注意的是，元动能量束能够到达的距离有限，大约在八格左右，并且无法穿过不透明的墙面。但玻璃或是其他的透明材料则允许元动能量束透过它们。为了将其正确地连接在一起，我需要确保元动节点间相距够近，并且不被墙壁阻挡。
如果我选中了已被界定连接方式的元动节点，那么我将能看到这些连接的可视化景象。任何向选中节点输入元动能量的节点都会呈现出红色的高亮选框，任何接收选中节点所发出的元动能量的节点则都会呈现出绿色的高亮选框。同时作为选定节点的输入和输出对象的特殊节点则会呈现出紫色的高亮选框。如果我完全不确定，我也能通过能束流动的方向判断元动能量的传递方向。
虽然元动谐振器可以界定节点间的连接方式，但如果没有蕴变元动能量实际被注入系统之中，那么什么也不会发生，这就要引入元动汲取仪这一节了。§l元动汲取仪§r
元动汲取仪是一种重要的元动节点，能够在放置到咒波裂隙附近时产生蕴变元动能量。其设计是在虚空吸管的基础上完成的，比起原型，元动汲取仪的顶部有一块致密的虚空金属板，用于抽入一般的元动能量（所幸这里无需下界之星，而虚空吸管对元动能量的唯一作用是将其凝聚为虚空种子），此外它还使用一个高速旋转的装置使元动能量蕴变化，并将其注入自身中心的元动宝石之中。元动汲取仪因此被视为蕴变元动能量产能系统的核心。当汲取仪从裂隙中抽取元动能量时，裂隙将会逐渐收缩并变得不稳定，就像使用虚空吸管时的效应一样。从一个小裂隙中抽取出的元动能量比大裂隙要少。因此，我需要时刻留意我正在抽取的裂隙，以确保其保持稳定并具有适当的尺寸。
元动汲取仪本身具有一个元动能量束输出槽，没有输入槽，因为它是产生蕴变元动能量的设备。因此，为了将能量从其中输出并进入其他元动节点，我只需手持元动谐振器潜行并右击汲取仪，然后右击其他的节点。
如果我想停用该设备，我只需向它提供红石信号即可。这会终止其抽取周围的裂隙以产生元动能量的进程，所以我可以借此确保我不会过度抽取一道咒波裂隙。§l元动中继器§r
元动中继器或许是最简易的元动节点，其唯一用途是传输元动能量束。它具有两个输入槽和两个输出槽，所以我可以用它来对能量传输系统进行路径调整。§l元动弥散仪§r
元动弥散仪可被视为元动汲取仪的反构装置，因为它会吸收蕴变元动能量并从顶部弥散出一般的元动能量。因此，它能用于为任何直接从咒波裂隙抽取能量的设备提供能量，例如安装了元动能量电池的护手或是虚空吸管。它具有一个输入槽，没有输出槽，毕竟它仅仅是消耗蕴变元动能量的装置。
我必须指出的是，弥散仪无法为元动汲取仪提供能量，因为它们会导致反馈故障，也即一般的元动能量被汲取仪转换为蕴变元动能量，然后后者又被弥散仪重新转化成前者，这样一来将会循环往复，无休无止。
还需要注意的是，使用这件装置为一般的元动设备充能，其实比从裂隙直接抽取效果更好。蕴变化进程显著地提高了元动能量产生的效率，所以即便是对我的以前的器械而言，我在全新的元动能量系统上所付出的努力也是完全值得的。
就像汲取仪一样，我能通过施加红石信号关闭弥散仪，如此一来即可终止其对一般元动设备的充能进程。
这些内容涵盖了蕴变元动能量系统的基础知识。尽管我已经取得了很大进展，但我很清楚我还有更多东西要学，有更多设备仍需制造，无论是传输元动能量的设备还是利用它们的设备。
这一领域如此具有潜能，我的脑海中不禁萦绕着数不胜数的新想法……

target:
就像所有的工人一样，牧羊人会在工作时升级。
 等级越高，牧羊人的速度就越快；他们的小屋等级和智力技能越高，他们升级就越快。

§a§nFlinger Yaw 
 
§rThis is the horizontal offset in degrees: 
 
- When the module faces horizontally, it's the offset left or right from that horizontal (X or Z) axis 
- When the module faces up or down, it's the offset from the vertical (Y) axis.  This is only useful if you also have a non-zero pitch.

- 如果模块朝向是竖直的，这表示相对于 Y 轴的夹角。仅当值非零时起效。

src:
To even get started with infusion crafting there are several things I will need: The Runic Matrix (which I now have), arcane pedestals and a ready supply of magic in the form of essentia.
Once you have your Runic Matrix properly placed into a structure commonly known as an Infusion Altar, you can begin to craft. The altar is crafted with the use of Salis Mundus, like most other mystical structures. Once the pillars have formed, the runic matrix can be activated using a casting tool.
The central pedestal located under the matrix is where the item you wish to infuse will go. You will also need several more pedestals placed around the altar where you can place the blocks and items you wish to infuse into the target object. Lastly you will need warded jars or similar essentia containers holding the requisite amount of vis.
Once all this is gathered you can click on the Runic Matrix with a casting tool to start the crafting process.
During the first stage of crafting, essentia will be drained from nearby sources. Crafting will stall if there is insufficient essentia available - something that you do not want and will be explained on following pages.
Once all the required essentia has been infused into the target object, the other objects will have their essential essence drained. Only when this is done will the crafting process complete.Infusion crafting is not without risks. The entire process involves forcing vast energies into a single object. Unpredictable things tend to happen.
Usually one of the fusion objects get knocked off a pedestal, or flux gets generated, but more catastrophic events are not unheard of.
The longer crafting continues due to unresolved problems like lack of vis or dropped items, the greater the chance of something bad happening.
These effects can be reduced by various means. Firstly you wish to keep the entire fusion structure as symmetrical as possible - take careful note of where you place pedestals and make sure they are balanced with other pedestals on the opposite side of the altar. When placing fusion items into them you may wish to keep them balanced as well. Lastly you can place occult paraphernalia around the altar in symmetrical formations (things like candles, skulls, etc.). These will have the effect of reducing instability.thaumcraft:textures/research/research5.png:128:0:128:136:1
target:
搭建注魔台前需要做如下准备：符文矩阵，奥术基座，以及足够数量的要素源质。
当你将符文矩阵正确地放置在一个名为注魔祭坛的神秘构造上后，便能够开始进行注魔合成。和其他奥术结构一样，注魔祭坛也可以通过世界盐来创建。完成搭建后，可以通过施法工具来启动符文矩阵。
符文矩阵下方，坐落于正中的基座是你用于放置被注魔物品的地方。你还需要环绕祭坛放置一些基座来放置被灌注的材料。最后你还需要在附近放置一些盛放了要素源质的罐子或者其他类似的魔力存储容器。
当一切就绪，你需要使用施法工具点击符文矩阵来开始注魔过程。
在这个过程的第一阶段，注魔祭坛将会从附近吸取所需的要素源质。
若没有足够的源质供应，注魔过程会中断 - 后文将会对这种你不希望发生的情况做进一步的阐释。
当所有需求的源质被灌入目标物品后，才能开始吸收被灌注的其他物品的要素源质。仅当这些都完成后注魔才能顺利完成。注魔合成并非毫无风险。其完整的过程实质上是把庞杂的魔法能量强制集中到单独的物品中，在这种情况下往往会发生一些不可预知的事情：
比较常见的意外包括注魔过载被基座中断掉，产生咒波等，但也可能遭遇一些闻所未闻的灾难事件。
由于魔力缺乏，物品掉落等未解决的问题导致而的注魔时间延迟越久，就越发有可能发生糟糕的事情。
可以有多种途径来减少这些意外的影响。首先你应该尽可能对称地布置注魔祭坛 - 一定要确保你放置的基座对侧有以祭坛为原点对称的基座与之平衡。当放置被灌注材料时，也需要尽可能保证放置位置对称与平衡。最后你可以环绕祭坛对称放置一些具有神秘属性的物品（比如蜡烛，头骨，水晶等），它们也能够减少注魔过程的风险。thaumcraft:textures/research/research5.png:128:0:128:136:1

src:
I may have made a mess of things. I have allowed flux to build up in the aura and now I need to get rid of it - fast.
Fortunately the answer might be found in one of the unique properties of flux. Technically flux is just 'dirty' vis, but what sets it apart is the fact that it can easily transform from a form of energy into physical matter. This makes it dangerous as it can spawn Taint and other forms of nastiness, but maybe it can also be coaxed into safer forms.
target:
我可能弄得一团糟了。我放任咒波在灵气场内聚集，但现在我需要尽快摆脱它。
幸运的是，解决方法可以利用咒波的特性。从技术上说，咒波是“被污染”的 Vis 。但不同的是它可以很轻易地从能量转化为物质。因为可以产生污点或其它污染的特性，它变得很危险。但也许它能够被诱导为更安全的形式。

src:
The Umancala's name derives from the words "Umano" and "Calamaro", respectively "Human" and "Squid". The squid part being obvious, the human attribute was given to it by its ancient discoverers when they mistook its flailing tentacles for a human swimmer's legs, used for propulsion in water.
That's where the similarities end, however. The Umancala is a bizarre looking medium sized Ictya, generally preying on smaller Ictya and seldom attacking us, unless very hungry. They hunt by generating extremely hot balls of boiling water which are then fired towards targets, akin to a Blaze's fireballs in the Nether.
target:
类人鱿（Umancala）的名字来自“Umano”和“Calamaro”，也即“人类”和“鱿鱼”。其名字中鱿鱼这部分不言自明，而人类的特征则源于这种生物的古代发现者，他们把其用于在水中推进的挥舞的触手误判为了人类游动的腿部。
但类人鱿与人类的相似之处仅限于此。它是一种形貌怪诞的中型渊鱼，通常猎食更小的渊鱼，很少袭击我们，除非是饥饿至极。它们捕猎时会发射炽热的沸水球，沸水球会被射向猎食的目标，与下界的烈焰人火球相似。
按下 Shift 查看更多

src:
I have managed to break down all my samples of primary and secondary essentia into a liquid state. The process has been slow and tedious however. Until I simplify the process it will never be practical for large scale usage.
Luckily extracting essentia from objects has a lot in common with the smelting of metals. Using a furnace as a base I might be able to create an essentia smeltery that automatically melts down items and separates out individual types of essentia.
target:
我已经将我所有的初级和次级源质分解为液态。然而这个过程缓慢又令人乏味。在我将这个过程简化之前，没有办法投入大规模使用。
幸运的是，从物品中提取源质与冶炼金属十分类似。使用熔炉作为基础应该能制作出一台自动分解物品并分离不同种类源质的源质冶炼厂。

src:
Pedestal is a fancy way of displaying your items, but at the same time it also allows some automation.

Coin of fortune - When active picks up items and XP and puts these in containers beside the pedestal, when inactive prevents players and pedestals with fortune coin from picking up items in its range
Hero's medallion - Acts as a tank for XP also when activated searches nearby pedestals for mending items and repairs those with its XP
Sword - Attacks mobs in its range (ignores bosses, tamed and child animals)
Bucket - milks cows and picks up fluids in the world and puts these in containers beside the pedestal
Shears - shears all shearable blocks and entities in its range
Fishing Rod - fishes for the player, doesn't pick up items or xp, you need to use something else for that
To turn on pedestal functionality either empty hand right click the switch or provide redstone signal or provide power remotely using redstone block or dust in another pedestal
target:
基座是一个花哨的显示你的物品的一种方式.但他同时也支持一些自动化

尝试将这些物品放在基座上，你会看到：
幸运硬币-我猜，物品不会躺在周围，如果有存储他们的容器的话

src: §r§rNote that it requires materials from the magic system. Instead of comparing two values or subtracting them, it multiplies and divides. Its two modes (changed with a right click) are multiplication and division. The symbol on the plate changes based on the mode. It multiplies (or divides) the value at the back by the largest input of its two sides. Notably, it can work with decimals or values greater than 15. The moment it outputs to redstone, however, it rounds to an integer and caps it at 15. To take advantage of the ability to use other values, Ratiators can take input from another Ratiator directly, avoiding capping and rounding.  It can measure things behind it like a comparator, but not through a solid block. Most comparator-readable things in Crossroads will be able to output decimals and numbers greater than 15 to a Ratiator. Shift right clicking a Ratiator with an Omnimeter displays the output.
target: §r§r需要注意，它需要来自魔法系统的材料。它不是比较两个值或减去它们，而是进行乘和除。它的两种模式（右击切换）是乘法模式和除法模式。求比器板上的符号会根据模式而变化。它将后面的值乘以（或除以）两边的最大输入。值得注意的是，它可以处理小数或大于15的数。然而，当它输出到红石信号的那一刻，输出值就会四舍五入为整数并将最大值限制在15。为了利用这种使用其</n>他值的能力，求比器可以直接从另一个求比器获取输入，避免封顶和四舍五入。它可以像一个比较器一样测量后方的东西，但不是通过一个固体方块。在十字路口中，大多数比较器可读的东西将能够向求比器输出小数和大于15的数字。手持万用表右击求比器将显示输出。

src:
I have discovered a way to manage the flux generated by the smelting process. By running the slurry through a secondary set of venting ports fitted with filters I am able to separate out the flux and safely vent it as harmless steam.
Like the slurry pumps, the vents need to be placed on the side of the smelter.
This process will reduce flux produced by about a third and additional vents will increase this, though there are diminishing returns.
target:
你还研究出一种管理冶炼过程中产生的咒波的方法.让源质黏浆流经源质过滤器的附加装置，就能够将咒波分离出来，将它变成安全无害的蒸汽排放出来.
就像粘液泵一样，这个排放口也要放在冶炼厂侧面。
还可以加装第三级装置来进一步减少咒波产量，但随着加装的排放口数量增多增加的效果会衰减。

src:
I have managed to put together a basic casting gauntlet and I am quite pleased with the result. It is still a bit rough, but that is to be expected from a prototype. Even as a prototype it will prove useful, allowing me to make delicate adjustments or alteration to thaumaturgical devices and safely manipulate them in all manner of ways.
My initial experiments have shown that it is only able to draw vis from a relatively small area around me. I should be careful not to deplete the aura.
My main stumbling block now is that in its current state it is little more than a magical wrench. Until I crack the secret of crafting foci its utility will be limited. The path before me is clear...
target:
我已经成功制作了一个施术用的护手，虽然看上去有些粗糙，不过我对此也是颇为满意的，毕竟它仅仅计划为一个原型装置。即使作为一个原型装置，它也意义非凡，它能够让我精确调整改造神秘使的装置，并且以各种安全的方式操纵它们。
我最初的实验表明，它只能从我周围的一小片区域中吸取Vis，我应该小心不要耗尽这片区域中所有的灵力。
目前，它不过是一个魔法扳手而已，面前最大的障碍就是如何破解制作核心的奥秘，否则它的效用将受到极大的限制。我面前的道路如今无比清晰……

src:
Mobs are captured via the Ender Shard and you need a full Ender Shard to generate a Mob Controller for that mob.

To initialise the Ender Shard with a mob, you need to quietly approach your chosen mob and hit it with the Ender Shard. The tooltip for that shard will then tell you the mob you have captured.

Now you have to fill the shard up, by killing that type of mob while the Ender Shard is in your toolbar. The tooltip will tell you how many you need to kill and the shard will glow when you have enough.
target:
为标记生物，你需要使用末影碎片，标记生物分两步走。

首先，悄悄接近你选择的生物，用末影碎片打它一下。

第二步，把末影碎片放在快捷栏里，杀死足够数量的生物以满足击杀数量。这可以在末影碎片的提示框中看到。杀够了之后，末影碎片会发光。

The Pumpjack Tower uses Flux/t to pump Crude Oil at a rate of mB/t. The produced oil is automatically ejected through the two side ports with orange dots.

The average Oil deposit will take days to deplete, though adding more Pumpjacks can speed the process.

Applying a redstone signal to the control panel will halt the machine's process, this behavior can be inverted by use of the Engineer's Hammer.
target:

一般，原油储藏会在一台泵连续工作 天后枯竭。自然地，使用多台泵会加快其枯竭速度。

src: The id of the target world dimension

These giant beetle creatures can be a challenge to fight without being aware of their battle tactics. The Emberback can be found flying towards its targets. Once near, the insect will drop down, expelling flaming hot air from under its shell. These insects are very smart, and can detect whether you’ve consumed a fire resistance potion, and will instead try to bite you for lower damage output. An easy way to take care of these bugs is either by using a shield, or by luring them to a body of water.
target: 在你不了解这种巨大的甲虫生物的情况下进行战斗是很有难度。余烬虫会径直飞向目标。一旦靠近，它就会下降，从甲壳中喷出炙热的气体。这种昆虫非常聪明，可以知道你是否使用了抗火药水，并且它会以较低的伤害输出咬你。对付这种昆虫的一种简单方法是使用盾牌，或者将它们引诱到水中。

src: Devil dust may bring adhesion, but its effects are negligible in its raw form. One of the easiest ways to make effects manifest in dust express themselves is to add gunpowder. src:
Most of my efforts in researching and experimenting with augment modifiers have been focused on passive effects. It may be prudent to try to come up with a system to actively increase my casting abilities while I am using it.
Normally, the flow of Vis through the gauntlet must be regulated to a slow rate, or the device will simply not work. If I am using this Vis frequently enough, it should be possible to slowly increase this limit whilst using the gauntlet. The main problem with this is that precisely monitoring such small differences in Vis usage is not the easiest thing to do, especially with the equipment available to me. But what if there was another way to indirectly measure my Vis usage?
I have considered one way to possibly make this work - during my recent studies in Golemancy, I have created the aggression module, which incites golems to attack other creatures. If I can somehow measure a reaction in the module when damaging something through focus casting, I might be able to use it as a signal to speed up the flow of Vis throughout the gauntlet. I should give my theory a try, but I doubt this will work like I am hoping it will.
target:
我在研究和试验调整器方面的大多数努力都集中在了被动效果上。尝试想出某种体系来在我使用法术时主动地增加我的施法能力，或许是精明之举。
一般来说，Vis在法师护手中的流动必须被调整到较低速率，否则装置可能因过载而无法正常工作。但如果我使用Vis足够频繁的话，应该就可以缓慢地提高法师护手中的流量上限。这么做主要的问题是，要精确地监控Vis用量的细微差异并非什么容易的事，对于我现在可以使用的装备而言尤其如此。但假如有其它方法可以间接检测我的Vis用量呢？
我已经想到了一种或许会起效的方法——在我最近对傀儡学的研究中，我制造出了一种攻击组件，用于驱使傀儡攻击其它的生物。如果我能以某种方式检测我在通过核心施法伤害某物时攻击组件中的反应，我也许可以使用它作为加速护手中Vis流动的提示信号。我应该将理论付诸实践，但我不知道这能否如我所希望的那样运作。
